            <text>
                <body>
                    <div xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xml:lang="nl" type="original">
<pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-orig-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>

<p xml:id="p.nl.1" n="1">Gij eet immers goed? Eet vooral maar zooveel brood als gij trek in hebt.<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> Wel te ruste, ik moet mijn laarzen gaan poetsen voor morgen.– </p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/></div>

                    <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                        <pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.1" n="1">You are eating well, aren’t you? Be sure and eat as much bread as you like.<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> Good-night, I have to go and polish my boots for tomorrow.</p>
                    </div>
                </body>
            </text>
            <standOff>
